-- Lower Saxony Calls for Government Grid Stake, Handelsblatt Says
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-05-02T05:28:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-02/lower-saxony-calls-for-government-grid-stake-handelsblatt-says.html
The German state of  Lower Saxony ’s
Prime Minister David McAllister said Germany’s government should
evaluate whether to part-nationalize the  power grid  to speed up
its expansion,  Handelsblatt  reported today, citing McAllister.  German Chancellor  Angela Merkel  and the Federal Network
Agency meet representatives from the  energy industry  today to
discuss the planned expansion of the grid, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
